%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E7%90%86%E5%90%91%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%81\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F23%2F10860%2F&amp;title=%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E9%82%BB%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%81%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%B8%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E7%90%86%E5%90%91%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%81\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F23%2F10860%2F&amp;title=%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E9%82%BB%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%81%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%B8%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E7%90%86%E5%90%91%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%EF%BC%81\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span></p>\n</p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[20534],"tags":[16910,8865,19196]}